<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0">
    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>The Secretary of State to the
                            Legation in Saudi Arabia</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1948v05p1</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d12</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">12</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1948-05-08T10:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1948-05-08T10:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-05-08T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-05-08T10:00:00-05:00" n="12" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d12">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">890F.6363/5–848: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Legation in Saudi Arabia</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret   us urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-05-08T11:00:00-04:00">May 8, 1948—11 a. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>171. Pls make clear to <gloss target="#t_SAG1">SAG</gloss> that <gloss target="#t_USG1">USG</gloss> feels the question of extent to which <gloss target="#t_Aramco1">Aramco</gloss> concession covers submerged Persian Gulf
                    area is matter for determination between <gloss target="#t_SAG1">SAG</gloss> and
                        <gloss target="#t_Aramco1">Aramco</gloss>. <gloss target="#t_USG1">USG</gloss> and UKG consultations not addressed to this problem but
                    confined to formulating applicable principles governing division Persian Gulf
                    submerged area (among countries having adjacent territory) with view to fair and
                    orderly exploitation. These principles will be submitted to <gloss target="#t_SAG1">SAG</gloss> when formulated.</p>
                <p>Sent Jidda, repeated London.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
